{
  "stem": "11964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is the first time I saw him crying, because he, he, he saw his family looking at him, being kicked by a boot of an SS man.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this reminds me of a story that Zvi Kolitz wrote.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's entitled Yossel Rakover, who was an Orthodox Jew, is being mistreated by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had just lost his wife and his children, murdered in his presence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there is a Gestapo man facing him with a dog right there at his heel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he realizes that the Gestapo man treats the dog better than he is being treated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he says, I was ashamed, in front of the dog, to be a man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I felt the same way about my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was ashamed in front of his children, how he was treated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we really were totally, totally committed to the proposition that we don't know how to deal with it, but we must deal with it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he may have been slow in exiting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was beaten because the SS didn't like the way he was moving about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this happened to me too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once they made a raid, and they wanted all the young women to come out and to scrub the floor in the mess hall with a toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A really small, small brushes, the size of a toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if we didn't work fast enough, they will hit us in the butt with a-- with a boot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would be kicked in the boot as we were on our hands and knees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and, you, you, you couldn't react.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a friend who, who was mistreated by an SS man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She went berserk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She went absolutely berserk, and she actually lost her mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
